quarterly or annual release cycles for a long time -- companies ship change=
s and improvements to their product and website every minute -- but user re=
search still typically works on a much slower cycle.&nbsp;</p><p style=3D"c=
olor: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">If y=
ou&#8217;ve worked in a customer facing or user research role, the standard=
